f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港沙士互相會<br />\n18 May 2016<br />\n病人組織：粵未及早通報致爆疫<br />\n<br />\n曾誤診為SARS而接受類固醇治療的香港沙士互助會會長林志釉稱，「絕對不同意是聯手抗疫」，他說，據上述報告，廣東省早於2002年11月已爆發SARS，甚至要寫報告，惟港方至2003年2月仍未獲得相關資訊，即使求問亦沒回覆，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為張德江今次講話避談當時是否沒主動通報，因而造成此後香港嚴重疫情爆發</span>，若談到共同取得勝利，那應向香港人有交代，為何當年不及早通知香港及世衛。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537eaff6ed7776d0bfd50a2ef65f865e096006ea","tid":247872,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5391f505be3f7adc18a910808967579832db3fe","tid":247872,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"其實八九民運, 香港人都有份參加<br />\n<br />\n唔係完全唔關香港人事"},{"pid":"2508d23a9703ada22298b21a6ab34a9c425c9563","tid":247872,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a373b355438d6c4468a1a6be3c0f93727c6aaea8","tid":247872,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"咁早就發功?"},{"pid":"9701b090fe2bf47144604fdfa57c10bee51d913f","tid":247872,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實八九民運, 香港人都有份參加<br />\n<br />\n唔係完全唔關香港人事</blockquote><br />\n64發生係支那，死既係支那人，爭取既係支那願景<br />\n咁關香港人乜春野事？<br />\n最多係俾香港人啟示，支共既醜惡<br />\n但講到底係搵香港人老襯"},{"pid":"38269e1ba7d71bbe192a99871ceaf7c281331ee7","tid":247872,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實八九民運, 香港人都有份參加<br />\n<br />\n唔係完全唔關香港人